==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''monocotyledon'''
# any plant belonging to the ''[[Monocotyledones]]'' (also written ''Monocotyledonae)'' or ''[[Liliopsida]]'', a class in the ''Angiospermae'', the [[flowering plant]]s. This group include the [[grass]]es, [[lilies]], [[orchid]]s and [[palm]]s.
